      <para id="id1171901081981">STEP 2: Preparation</para>
      <para id="id1171905603167">As soon as the songs have been accepted, all the learners are given the opportunity to listen to the songs and to learn certain sections of the songs. An adjudicator must know the songs to be able to adjudicate! Each group must provide the following for their song:</para>
      <list id="id1171901387552" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>A recording by the original artist</item>
        <item>Backtrack</item>
        <item>Photocopies of the lyrics for the rest of the learners to paste into their journals</item>
      </list>
      <para id="id1171905451974"><emphasis effect="bold">Homework:</emphasis> Each group or solo singer practises individually.</para>
